{"type": "article", "id": 16621, "title": "Bloom Brush", "description": "", "date": "2015-10-27T06:00:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606143122mZF2cisMdlyNPvLu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一根外形酷似一个花苞的马桶刷，刷子的毛是包在内侧的。使用时需要用力向下压，将刷子的两侧翻开，然后清洁马桶。蓝色和绿色的外观给人清新自然的感受，经过清理的马桶刷可以直接立在地面上，不会影响屋里的整齐美观。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143935GfwXqQVyOKvcRFMC.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"611\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.9546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143936NbyzYPeEsag5tkBQ.jpg\" width=\"640\" height=\"234\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.365625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}